        "description": "<p>Handbuild Your Own Mini Local Delights in Ceramic<br><br>Celebrate local heritage through clay in this hands-on session where you’ll sculpt and decorate 6 ceramic magnets shaped like beloved traditional kueh - from ang ku kueh,Tutu Kueh and more.<br><br>Using air dry clay and paint on the ceramic pieces, you’ll create charming food inspired keepsakes that are both playful and functional. Magnets will be attached after the pieces are dry<br><br>No experience needed, perfect for family events and bonding with your loved ones!</p>",
