        "price": null,
        "description": "<p>Get an exclusive behind-the-scenes look at The Gentlemen’s Press with our Studio Visit & Walkthrough Experience. This guided verbal tour will take you through our creative process, giving you insight into how our beautiful stationery and prints are made.<br />During this intimate session, you'll be walked through the different machines and techniques that make our work unique. From our iconic letterpress to foil stamping, embossing, die-cutting, and more, our team will explain the artistry and craftsmanship behind every print. It’s the perfect opportunity to discover how our pieces come to life.<br /><br /><strong>What’s Included:</strong></p><ul><li><p>A 1.5 hour personalised, guided walk-through of our studio</p></li><li><p>In-depth explanations of our machines and print techniques</p></li><li><p>The chance to ask questions and get insight into the printing process</p></li><li><p>All participants of the studio visit will receive a small gift token - a little keepsake to remember your time with us.</p></li></ul><p><br />Book your visit today and see where the magic happens!</p>",
