        "category": null,
        "price": null,
        "description": "<p>Paint whatever you like, no experience needed. We’ll provide reference images, or you can bring your own.<br />This beginner-friendly gouache session is a gentle introduction to painting. You’ll learn what gouache is, how to use it, and how to mix simple colours with confidence. We’ll guide you through easy techniques like layering and blending, step by step.<br />You can choose to paint a simple still life, a landscape, or follow your own idea. It’s all about having a go in a relaxed, supportive space where you can explore and enjoy the process at your own pace.<br /><br />Each participant will complete one gouache painting on paper to take home.<br /><br /><br /><strong>Workshop Duration: </strong>2.5 Hours<br /><br /><strong>About Artify Studio</strong><br />Established in 2014, Artify Studio offers a range of art services from children and adult art classes, corporate team-building sessions to community outreach programmes.<br /><br /><strong>Venue Information </strong></p><ul><li><p>Only lifts 7 or 8 provide access to our studio. Please press the\"12/13\"button.</p></li><li><p>Parking is available within the building.</p></li><li><p>Nearest MRT - Nicoll Highway (CC 5) / Lavender (EW 11)</p></li><li><p>Nearby buses - 107, 961, 980 (Jalan Sultan); 7, 32, 51, 61, 63, 80, 145,175, 197 (North Bridge Road), 100, 961, 980 (Beach Road)</p></li></ul>",
