        "price": null,
        "description": "<p><strong>Peranakan Tiles Clay Accessories Workshop</strong><br>Inspired by the vibrant motifs of Peranakan tiles, this beginner-friendly workshop will show you how to turn clay into unique, wearable art pieces that are full of personality.<br><br><strong>What you’ll learn:</strong><br>▫️ Simple floral sculpting techniques<br>▫️ Tricks to create eye-catching outline details for Peranakan Tiles design<br>▫️ How to assemble your pieces into ready-to-wear accessories<br><br><strong>What you’ll take home:</strong><br>▫️ 1-2 of your very own handcrafted accessories - choose to make earrings, hair clips, necklaces, bracelets, brooch pins or keychains, all designed by you! (Quantity is dependent on individual's pace)<br>Come for the crafting, stay for the joy of making something beautiful that you’ll actually love to wear (or gift!).<br><br>Drop us an email at <a href=\"mailto:sales@theassembly.space\" rel=\"nofollow\">sales@theassembly.space</a> for other enquiries.</p>",
