        "id": "merged:23997dd8f9f8ff91425d0592c12bd653673fbbaac97fc4a98575710aa18a717f",
        "title": "<p>Blooming Together: a watercolour workshop on the national flower</p>",
        "startDateTime": "Sat, 10 Jan 2026",
