        "description": "<p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">Experience the enchanting ambiance of live jazz music in Singapore at The Lobby Lounge, Frasers House, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Singapore, every Friday and Saturday evening. Whether unwinding after a long day or seeking a memorable night out in Bugis, let talented musicians serenade you with soulful melodies in an elegant lounge setting.<br><br>The Lobby Lounge offers an immersive evening where captivating performances meet crafted cocktails, fine wines, and curated bites. Each night unfolds as a harmonious blend of music, atmosphere, and indulgence - creating a truly unforgettable jazz night experience in Singapore.<br><br>📅<strong>Dates </strong>: Every Friday and Saturday<br>🕒<strong>Time </strong>: 8:00pm to 10:30pm<br>📍<strong>Location </strong>: The Lobby Lounge, Frasers House, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Singapore<br><br><strong>Standard Admission</strong><br><strong>•&nbsp;</strong>$38 (Entrance Ticket only)<br><strong>V.I.P Admission&nbsp;</strong><br>• $68 (Entrance Ticket with a glass of Champagne)<br><br><strong>🎼 July Line-up</strong><br>• 03 &amp; 04 July - Alemay Fernandez &amp; Todd Hardy<br>• 10 &amp; 11 July - Jacintha<br>• 17 &amp; 18 July - Michelle Poh<br>• 24 &amp; 25 July - James Flynn<br>• 31 July - Reggie Pryor<br><br><strong>🎼 August Line-up</strong><br>• 01 August - Reggie Pryor<br>• 07 &amp; 08 August - Jacintha<br>• 14 &amp; 15 August - Namie Rasman<br>• 21 &amp; 22 August - James Flynn<br>• 28 &amp; 29 August - Wendy Tan</p>",
