        "description": "A Gentle & Creative Movement Workshop for Seniors<br><br>\"Hopscotch\" Like the Immortals is a creative movement workshop specially designed for seniors interested in dance to explore expressive movement at a safe and comfortable pace.<br><br>Inspired by the legend of the Eight Immortals and traditional festival dances like the masked Nuo dance, this workshop transforms ancient rhythms into simple, fun, and easy-to-follow steps. A unique \"hopscotch\" pattern on the floor will serve as your creative guide for gentle and steady footwork - absolutely no jumping or leaping required!<br><br>This is the perfect opportunity to try out dance, experience new ways to move to a rhythm, and meet new friends interested in dance.<br><br>⏳ What to expect in 60 minutes:<br>15 Mins - Gentle Group Warm-Up<br>45 Mins - Guided Creative movement workshop<br><br>💡 Good to know:<br><br>- No dance experience required: This is a safe space to try contemporary dance for the first time. All movements are low-impact and adaptable to your comfort level.<br>- Bilingual Session: Conducted in both English and Mandarin.<br>- Facilitators: Professional dancers from The Arts Fission Company.<br>- Attire: Please come in loose, comfortable clothing.<br>- Mindset: Bring an open mind and enjoy an engaging movement experience.<br><br> -  -  -  -  - <br><br>乐龄温和创意肢体律动工作坊 <br><br>《跳八仙》是一项专为对舞蹈感兴趣的乐龄人士设计的创意肢体律动工作坊。让您在安全、舒适且轻松的节奏中，尽情探索身体流动的乐趣。<br><br>工作坊的灵感源自古老神秘的傩舞及广为人知的“八仙”传奇。我们将传统的喜庆节奏转化为简单、好玩且易学的舞步。地板上精心设计的独特“跳飞机”图案，将化身为您的创意指南，带领您进行温和且平稳的漫步与踏步 - 全程绝对不需要任何跳跃动作！<br><br>这不仅是您尝试舞蹈、体验全新律动方式的绝佳机会，还能让您结识志同道合的新朋友，一起快乐舞动。<br><br>⏳ 1小时精彩流程：<br>15分钟 - 温和集体暖身<br>45分钟 - 导师指引创意肢体律动<br><br>💡 报名须知：<br><br>- 无需任何舞蹈基础：这是一个让您首次安心尝试现代舞的安全空间。所有动作皆属低冲击性，可根据您的舒适度随时调整。<br>- 双语授课：现场将以中英语温馨互动。<br>- 专业导师：由化生艺术团的专业舞者带领。<br>- 活动着装：请穿着宽松、舒适的衣裤。<br>- 带着轻松的心情：保持开放的心态，尽情享受这场别开生面的肢体探索之旅！",
        "organizer": null,
