        "coordinates": {
          "lng": 103.89676240426208,
          "lat": 1.3164631078694682
        },
        "category": null,
        "price": null,
        "description": "<p>Discover the hilarious and engaging art of caricature drawing with Kamal Dollah, founder of <a href=\"http://www.cartoon.sg\">www.cartoon.sg</a> and Kamal Arts (<a href=\"http://www.kamal.sg\">www.kamal.sg</a>).<br /><br />This two-hour programme introduces the artform and systematically guides you through the essential techniques and observational skills needed to capture personality and likeness with a playful, exaggerated twist. Whether you're a budding artist or hobbyist, acquire a fun new skill, with the perfect opportunity to learn from a master.<br /><br />The ability to draw caricatures by raw observation and by hand is still a rare and remarkable skill that embodies personal perception, wit, and spontaneity - qualities that no AI algorithm can fully replicate. It reflects not just technical prowess but a deep understanding of human expression, allowing for a level of satire, exaggeration, and charm that resonates uniquely with viewers.</p>",
