        "description": "<p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><em>This is Home</em> is a 60-minute <strong>beginner-friendly workshop</strong> that invites participants to celebrate Singapore’s spirit through the beloved National Day song <em>“Home”</em> by Kit Chan. Using <strong>guitar</strong> and <strong>cajón</strong>, participants will learn simple chords and rhythms before coming together in an uplifting group jam.<br><br>Blending music-making with a short reflection on Singapore’s history, the session fosters joy, unity, and national pride. All instruments are provided, making it accessible to youths, seniors, and underserved communities alike.</p>",
