        "price": null,
        "description": "<p>Transversal Winds: A Free-Reed Dialogue is a collaboration between Resonance &amp; Kebun Bahru CC Harmonica Ensemble. This concert features the Chinese sheng and the Western harmonica. Through a blend of traditional repertoire, contemporary works, and local arrangements, this concert invites audiences to discover the rich and distinctive sounds of both instruments while exploring how they continue to evolve.</p>",
