        "category": null,
        "price": null,
        "description": "<p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">Acrylic Floral Painting - Paint A Bloom<br><br>Take a break from the everyday and enjoy a relaxing, creative experience with&nbsp;<strong>Acrylic Floral Painting - Paint A Bloom</strong>.&nbsp;<br>This adult-friendly workshop invites participants to explore the beauty of floral art while discovering how contemporary artists use colour, texture, and expressive brushwork to bring nature-inspired subjects to life.<br><br>Inspired by the works of Singapore artists, this session offers an opportunity to appreciate how flora and natural elements continue to influence Singapore’s vibrant visual arts scene.<br><br>Whether you are looking to try something new, spend a meaningful afternoon with friends, or simply unwind through art, this workshop provides a welcoming space to connect with creativity. Participants will leave with their own completed floral artwork and a deeper appreciation of acrylic painting as a contemporary art form.<br><br><strong>No prior art experience is required. All materials will be provided.</strong><br>Perfect for adults who enjoy creative activities, exploring art, or discovering new cultural experiences through the&nbsp;<strong>SG Culture Pass</strong>. 🌸🎨</p>",
