        "description": "<p><strong>Sentosa 4D AdventureLand</strong>, Sentosa's high-tech interactive entertainment zone is home to a diverse and exciting collection of highly sensorial experiences at Imbiah Lookout.<br /><br /><strong>‘Chaos In Wonderland’</strong>, an immersive 4D show experience where you become part of the show through a synchronisation of this wide spectrum of special visual, sound, motion and 4D effects. Join Ed and Edda at the amusement park which turns into a crazy night of chaos with now living dinosaurs, pirates and other fairy tale characters!<br /><br />The 4D motion-simulated, <strong>‘Extreme Log Ride’</strong> is where you will be riding through ravines and down valleys in a virtual “roller coaster”. In addition, <strong>‘Haunted Mine Ride 4D’</strong> promises riders a fast and exhilarating adventure as you plunge headfirst into an old dilapidated gold mine that just happens to be haunted.<br /><br /><strong>‘Desperados’</strong>, the first 4D interactive shoot-out game in Asia offers a superior gaming experience. Ride on a motion-based saddles to take out bandits with your hand-held laser guns.</p>",
