        "description": "Crafty Corner at Ancourage is a creative arts and crafts class designed especially for children aged 3-5. Through themed, step-by-step art projects, children explore painting, collage, texture, and mixed materials while building important developmental skills.<br>Each lesson introduces young learners to hands-on art making in a fun and supportive environment. Children experiment with different materials such as paint, paper, clay, and collage. Our classes are carefully designed to support early childhood development, helping children strengthen fine motor coordination, creativity, and confidence through art.<br>At Ancourage, we believe creativity grows best in small, supportive classes where every child has the space to explore and enjoy the creative process.<br>Lessons can be booked as one-off sessions or multi-class packages, giving parents the flexibility to try a class or continue regularly.<br>",
