        "title": "Singapore National Monuments Walking Tour",
        "startDateTime": "2026-07-13T08:30:00+08:00",
        "endDateTime": "2026-07-13T11:30:00+08:00",
        "dateText": "2026-07-13",
        "timeText": "08:30 - 11:30",
        "venue": "CITY HALL MRT STATION",
        "venueVerified": true,
        "address": null,
        "coordinates": {
          "lng": 103.8543591714802,
          "lat": 1.2948849000552567
        },
        "category": null,
        "price": null,
        "description": "Starting at the iconic Raffles Hotel, you’ll stroll through 12 must-see landmarks in a compact 2.5 to 3 km loop. Discover colonial-era gems like the Former City Hall, where WWII’s end was sealed, and immerse yourself in the serenity of historic temples, including Thian Hock Keng and Sri Mariamman Temple. Then, admire an eclectic mix of Gothic spires, neoclassical columns, and vibrant temple gopurams, reflecting Singapore’s multicultural history. This experience is perfect for history buffs, culture lovers, and photography enthusiasts, offering a deep dive into the city’s past. With a comfortable pace and plenty of opportunities to snap photos, this tour seamlessly blends history, culture, and architecture.",
        "organizer": null,
        "eventUrl": "https://www.catch.sg/Event/Singapore-National-Monuments-Walking-Tour-20250821090655",
