        "schemaVersion": "1.0",
        "id": "merged:a01a456a1a63559b287d6b9012f5c8b30ed004759e63e40e498faf88a3b59e47",
        "title": "MONOPOLY: HIDDEN Singapore - Love, Lost & Found",
        "startDateTime": "2026-07-13T10:00:00+08:00",
        "endDateTime": "2026-07-13T18:00:00+08:00",
        "dateText": "2026-07-13",
        "timeText": "10:00 - 18:00",
        "venue": "SINGAPORE MANAGEMENT UNIVERSITY (SCHOOL OF ACCOUNTANCY)",
        "venueVerified": true,
        "address": null,
        "coordinates": {
          "lng": 103.84973498388698,
          "lat": 1.2957630175515251
        },
        "category": null,
        "price": null,
        "description": "⭐ Inspired by the classic board game and brought to life with HIDDEN’s signature storytelling, MONOPOLY: HIDDEN Singapore turns the city into an in-world adventure. Hit the streets with Mr. Monopoly and his cheeky companion, Void Deck Cat, as Singapore’s neighbourhoods become living MONOPOLY boards. Every corner hides a story. Discover hidden gems, uncover forgotten histories, and unlock surprise rewards in this first-of-its-kind experience. <br><br>With the FIRST adventure in the series - Love, Lost & Found - explore Singapore’s hidden treasures as you embark on an adventure interwoven in a heartwarming love story.<br><br>Mr. Monopoly has stumbled upon a forgotten bundle of old, handwritten love letters; yellowed pages whispering of romance and intrigue. Who penned these letters? And to whom were they written? A story of passion and secrecy is hidden in plain sight across Singapore's historical and charming landmarks. But there's a catch: to unseal the letters, you need to prove yourself to the enigmatic Void Deck Cat, who knows Singapore's secrets better than any human. Her puzzles and riddles are crafted to delight and intrigue explorers of all levels. This Monopoly edition isn't just about locations; it's about rediscovering love hidden in history, finding what was lost, and celebrating what's newly found. Get your tickets for MONOPOLY: HIDDEN Singapore!",
        "organizer": null,
        "eventUrl": "https://www.catch.sg/Event/MONOPOLY-HIDDEN-Singapore-Love-Lost-Found-20260112055831",
        "isOnline": false,
        "parentEventId": "/Event/MONOPOLY-HIDDEN-Singapore-Love-Lost-Found-20260112055831",
